KEY FEATURES
============

✓ Zero setup - no API keys for most sources (FRED instant free)
✓ Idempotent - safe to run multiple times
✓ Error handling - network timeouts, 404s, rate limits
✓ Compression - ZSTD format, efficient storage
✓ Validation - data quality checks + markdown report
✓ Full history - 6+ years of OHLCV available
✓ Docker ready - works in backtester image

FRED API KEY (2 MINUTES)
========================

1. Visit: https://fred.stlouisfed.org/docs/api/api_key.html
2. Click "Request API Key"
3. Sign up (free email)
4. Copy key
5. Export: export FRED_API_KEY=your_key_here
   Or save in .env: FRED_API_KEY=your_key_here

RELATED FILES
=============

Full report: .result/backtest/v4/phase4_scripts_report.md
QA output: docs/data_quality_report.md (generated by validator)

SUPPORT
=======

For each script issue, see README.md Troubleshooting section.

Most common issues:
- "No module" error → pip install httpx pandas pyarrow
- HTTP 404 on old data → normal, script skips automatically
- FRED rate limit → wait 60 seconds, auto-retry
- Empty data → check internet, verify API endpoints online

